title: Made it so that when a user filters the MachineFragment too much (for example,…
message:
Made it so that when a user filters the MachineFragment too much (for example, unchecks all filters) they are notified that the filters are not allowing anything to be displayed.

Ie. It alerts the user that there are MACHINES in the list, just none that fit their criteria.

title: Made the LocationActivity only show the loading progress bar when the list…
message: Made the LocationActivity only show the loading progress bar when the list begins empty. The data in the app is generally valid for a few minutes at a time, so clearing the list while refreshing isnt necessary. List is only cleared when the new data is retrieved. SwipeToRefresh loading icon does show however because its unobtrusive.

title: Made the app pop a snackbar if there is an error loading the data. This is…
message:
Made the app pop a snackbar if there is an error loading the data. This is defined as anything coming from Retrofit's onFailure callback.

A snackbar is passive enough, and it doesnt need to clear the data if there is a failure, since the data we pull down is valid for a few minutes at a time. Therefore showing an error or empty view doesnt make sense in most cases.
